Tho mar Ahazia


1  Kane Ahab osetho, jo-Moab nodagi bet e bwo loch Israel. 
2  Chieng’ moro Ahazia nogore piny koa e dirisa mar gorofa mar ode man Samaria, mohinyore. Nooro joote mondo odhi openj Baal-zebub nyasach Ekron kata kobiro kwo. 
3  To malaika mar Ruoth Nyasaye nowacho ni Elija ja-Tishbe niya, “Dhi irom gi joote mag ruodh Samaria, kendo ipenjgi nia, ‘Nyasaye onge e Israel ka koso, momiyo udhi mana ir Baalzebub mondo upenje wach? 
4  Emomiyo Ruoth Nyasaye owacho ni ok nikwo, to initho mana e kitandani minindoeno.’ ”


5  Kane jootego odok ir ruoth, nopenjogi gimomiyo giduogo. 
6  Ne gidwoke niya, “Ng’at moro oromo kodwa, mowachonwa ni mondo wadog ir ruoth ma noorowa, wanyise ni Ruoth Nyasaye owacho kama: ‘Nyasaye onge Israel koso, momiyo ioro ji ir Baalzebub nyasach Ekron mondo ipenje wach? Kuom mano ok nikwo, to iinitho manaa e kitanda minindoeno.’ ” 
7  Ruoth nopenjogi niya, “Jal moromo kodu, monyisou wechego, chal nadi?” 
8  

Ne gidwoke ni, “Norwako law ma rayier, kendo notweyo okanda mar del e nungone.” Ahazia nowacho ni, “Kara en Elija ja-Tishbe.”


9  Eka ruoth nooro jatend lweny mane nigi jolweny piero abich mondo odhi ir Elija. Jatelono noyude kobet piny ewi got moro. Nowachone niya, “Ng’at Nyasaye, ruoth owacho ni mondo ilor!” 
10  

To Elija nodwoke ni, “Ka an ng’at Nyasaye adier, to mach mondo oa e polo, otieki kaachiel gi jogi piero abichgo.” Eka mach noa e polo motieko jalo gi joge.


11  Ruoth nochako ooro ni Elija jatelo machielo kod joge piero abich. Jalo nodhi ir Elija, mowachone niya, “Ng’at Nyasaye, ruoth owacho ni mondo ilor piyo!” 
12  To Elija nodwoke ni, “Ka an ng’at Nyasaye adier, to mach mondo oa e polo, otieki kaachiel gi jogi.” Mi mach noa e polo, motieke gi joge.


13  Eka ruoth nooro jatelo mar adek kod joge piero abich. Jatelono nodhi, mogoyo chonge piny e nyim Elija, kosaye niya, “Yaye ng’at Nyasaye, akwayi ni mondo ngimana kod ngima ji piero abichgi obedni ka gima igeno e chunyi. 
14  Wasewinjo kaka mach noa e polo monego jotelo ariyogo, kaachiel gi jogi mag lweny, to koro mondo ngimana obedni ka gima igeno e chunyi.” 
15  Eka malaika mar Ruoth Nyasaye nowacho ni Elija niya, “Lor kode, kik iluore.” Omiyo nolor, mi ne gidhi kode ir ruoth. 
16  Eka Elija nowacho ni ruoth niya, “Ruoth Nyasaye owacho kama: ‘Ok nikwo, to initho mana e kitanda minindoeno, nikech nioro joote ir Baalzebub nysach Ekron mondo ipenje wach.’ ”


17  Omiyo Ahazia notho kaka Ruoth Nyasaye nomiyo Elija owacho. Joram owadgi nodoko ruoth kare e higa mar ariyo mar loch Jehoram wuod Jehoshafat, ruodh Juda, nikech Ahazia ne onge gi wuowi. 
18  Timbe moko duto mag Ahazia ondik e kitap Weche Mag ndalo mag Ruodhi mag Israel.

